00:15:15.260 --> 00:15:17.260
he will say, "I want to horsing."

00:15:17.260 --> 00:15:20.260
Now, "horsing" is going for a horse ride.

00:15:20.260 --> 00:15:23.260
So, Parusharam comes to my office every day.

00:15:23.260 --> 00:15:26.260
He comes for a tummy rub,

00:15:26.260 --> 00:15:28.260
because he believes that will give me luck. (Laughter)

00:15:28.260 --> 00:15:31.260
When I started Parikrma

00:15:31.260 --> 00:15:35.260
I began with a great deal of arrogance

00:15:35.260 --> 00:15:37.260
of transforming the world.

00:15:37.260 --> 00:15:40.260
But today I have been transformed.

00:15:40.260 --> 00:15:42.260
I have been changed with my children.

00:15:42.260 --> 00:15:45.260
I've learned so much from them:

00:15:45.260 --> 00:15:48.260
love, compassion, imagination

00:15:48.260 --> 00:15:51.260
and such creativity.

00:15:51.260 --> 00:15:55.260
Parusharam is Parikrma

00:15:55.260 --> 00:15:58.260
with a simple beginning but a long way to go.

00:15:58.260 --> 00:16:00.260
I promise you, Parusharam

00:16:00.260 --> 00:16:04.260
will speak in the TED conference a few years from now.

00:16:04.260 --> 00:16:06.260
Thank you.

00:16:06.260 --> 00:16:17.260
(Applause)

